reviewText: Disc can't even get through the first movie without stopping due to scratches.

I have all the Neverending Story movies and this one is as good as the others. The Never Ending Story is about a boy and a book. As he has adventures they appear in the book. IN this adventure, some evil nasties get the book and make his life miserable but he has a great revenge at the end.  But the movie I bought the set for was A Wrinkle in Time. I wateched it twice already! It is about the children of a man who disappears. They must search for him in time. The adventures they have in finding him and bringing him home are magical.
haven't watched yet but product was good
I want this for the $19.99 price don't want to pay 30. I'd reorder it at the $20 dollar price
Good bunch of movies to watch!
